### Crear un nuevo usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user  HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "exampleEmail@gmail.com",
	"password":"12341234Abc",
	"phone":"+34 123456789"
}

### Relizar un login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/login  HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "exampleEmail@gmail.com",
	"password":"12341234Abc",
}

